{"id":45940,"type":4,"name":"Green Beret","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/e9/40/45940_a6Gsu.jpg","rating":{"total":85,"count":{"1":1,"2":1,"3":1,"4":0,"5":2,"6":13,"7":31,"8":27,"9":8,"10":1},"score":7.2},"summary":"绿色兵团是由日本KONAMI（科乐美）公司在1987年推出的一款FC游戏作品。游戏不论是人物设定、场景设定以及是任务等等都有着深厚的冷战时代色彩（比如第二关、第四关、第六关敌人的红军毡帽；第一关背景的雪山以及第四关、第五关背雪松，这些都有着鲜明的苏联特色。而最后要摧毁的那座核弹装置，更是折射冷战时代美苏双方争端的焦点——核武器）。游戏中你肩负摧毁敌人秘密武器的使命，随身携带一把刺刀（匕首），深入敌军内部，与敌人周旋作战。正因为具有这个特征，中国大陆很多资深玩家曾冠名该游戏为“拼刀子”。 ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>绿色兵团</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/747\">KONAMI</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/747\">KONAMI</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>グリーンベレー</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Rush'n Attack</li><li><span>平台: </span>街机</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>XBOX 360</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>FC</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>ACT</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1~2</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>1985年7月</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":119,"on_hold":1,"dropped":3},"tags":[{"name":"FC","count":35},{"name":"Konami","count":13},{"name":"ACT","count":11},{"name":"童年","count":6},{"name":"救人质","count":2},{"name":"1995","count":2},{"name":"无限命","count":2},{"name":"Family_Computer","count":1},{"name":"平台动作游戏","count":1},{"name":"七星","count":1},{"name":"汉化","count":1},{"name":"1985","count":1},{"name":"Platform","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":747,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/bb/c1/747_prsn_43cah.jpg","name":"科乐美","desc":"开发"}],"like":[{"id":9544,"name":"超级魂斗罗","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b2/30/9544_WXwb5.jpg"},{"id":9575,"name":"炸弹人FC版","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/4d/8b/9575_iQejH.jpg"},{"id":46125,"name":"高桥名人的冒险岛","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/19/10/46125_u5c0p.jpg"},{"id":9543,"name":"魂斗罗","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/73/64/9543_k3wnd.jpg"},{"id":46110,"name":"马戏团","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/bc/19/46110_Hqv2v.jpg"},{"id":2736,"name":"超级马力欧兄弟","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/47/fd/